Central Bank Digital Currency
1.1 Subject and Purpose of the Technical Guideline

Objective Covered by Rationale
Cre.Obj.1 Cre.Req.1 Cre.Obj.1 requires that the issuer can create valid CBDC notes, which is 
covered by Cre.Req.1.
Cre.Obj.2 Cre.Req.2 Cre.Obj.2 requires that only the issuer can create valid CBDC notes, 
which is directly covered by Cre.Req.2.
Cre.Obj.3 Cre.Req.4 Cre.Obj.3 requires the existence of a logging process, which is directly 
covered by Cre.Req.4.
